    • addDorse

      protected void addDorse()
      Add a DORSE in this cell, no matter what the zCoord of this cell is.

      This is intended to perform the effect of the Card Atlas

      See Also:
      PlayerAtlas

    • addBlock

      protected Block addBlock()
      Add a new block in this cell; this is only based on the zCoord of the cell;

      zCoord = 0 ----> Block B1

      zCoord = 1 ----> Block B2

      zCoord = 2 ----> Block B3

      zCoord = 3 ----> Block DORSE

      Returns:
      The Block just added in this cell

    • moveWorkerInto

      protected java.lang.Boolean moveWorkerInto​(Worker w)
      Move the worker passed as parameter in this cell. Also mark the old Cell of the worker as free.

      The function doesn't check if this cell is empty or not

      Parameters:
      w - The worker you want to move in this cell
      Returns:
      true if w != null ; false otherwise
